column_description: Unique id of the feedback form.
Timestamp of when the feedback form was completed.
Timestamp of when the feedback form was created.
Foreign key referencing the USER who completed and submitted the feedback.
Timestamp of when the feedback form was deleted.
Foreign key referencing the INTERVIEW for which the feedback is directed.
Overall rating (1-4 scale) to the candidate.
Foreign key referencing the TEMPLATE_FIELD that this form used.
Form title. This can be edited in Feedback and Form Settings.
Form type. Feedback forms are of type interview.
Foreign key referencing the OPPORTUNITY that the candidate was interviewed for.
